# Ejercicio 11
```
Sube un 5% el salario a los 3 empleados que menos cobran
```
```mysql
UPDATE empleados 
SET salario=salario*1.05
WHERE id IN (
			SELECT id FROm (
                			SELECT id FROM empleados 
                			ORDER BY salario ASC 
                			LIMIT 3
) as temp
)
```
```mysql
-- ESTUDIAR-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
UPDATE empleados e
JOIN (
    SELECT id FROM empleados ORDER BY salario ASC LIMIT 3
) t ON e.id = t.id
SET e.salario = e.salario * 1.05;
```
